data.title: Baseball Positions
data.meta_description: Rosters WBC - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document contains lists of baseball players with their pitching handedness, height, weight, and date of birth. It includes sections for pitchers, catchers, infielders, and outfielders from various countries and regions including Latin America, Asia, Taiwan, and the Dominican Republic. Over 100 players are listed with their relevant statistics.
